Gold. I charge 2 EV's for $0. And my solar panels paid themselves off 5 years ago. I'm on the 
@OVOEnergy_AU
 EV charging plan, they're great. 11am-2pm is 0c/kWH - yep, zero. I also pump energy in to my home battery (also paid for itself), this gets me through peak tariff time.

